#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:2
msgid "基准测试"
msgstr "Benchmarking"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:5
msgid "准备环境"
msgstr "Prepare the Environment"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:7
msgid "假设你已经 fork 仓库并 clone 到了本地。"
msgstr "Assuming you have forked the repository and cloned it locally."

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:9
msgid "使用 ``cd JAnim`` 进入项目文件夹，然后安装包含基准测试所需依赖的环境："
msgstr ""
"Use ``cd JAnim`` to enter the project folder, then install the environment with dependencies required for benchmarking:"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:11
msgid "pip install -e .[bench]"
msgstr "pip install -e .[bench]"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:16
msgid "运行基准测试"
msgstr "Run Benchmarks"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:18
msgid "项目提供了一个方便的脚本入口来运行基准测试。命令格式为："
msgstr "The project provides a convenient script entry point to run benchmarks. The command format is:"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:20
msgid "python scripts bench [options]"
msgstr "python scripts bench [options]"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:24
msgid "可用选项示例："
msgstr "Examples of available options:"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:26
msgid "``--untested_tags``：测试自 v2.1.0 之后所有尚未测试的 tag。"
msgstr "``--untested_tags``: test all untested tags since v2.1.0."

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:27
msgid "``--tags <tag> [<tag> ...]``：按一或多个标签运行测试，例如 ``--tags v2.1.0 v2.2.0``。"
msgstr "``--tags <tag> [<tag> ...]``: run tests for one or more tags, for example ``--tags v2.1.0 v2.2.0``."

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:28
msgid "``--hashes <hash> [<hash> ...]``：按提交哈希运行测试（可传入多个）。"
msgstr "``--hashes <hash> [<hash> ...]``: run tests by commit hash (multiple values allowed)."

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:29
msgid "``-o`` / ``--open``：自动在浏览器中打开预览。"
msgstr "``-o`` / ``--open``: automatically open the preview in the browser."

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:32
msgid "运行示例"
msgstr "Usage Examples"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:34
msgid "测试所有未测试的 tag（在 v2.1.0 之后）："
msgstr "Test all untested tags (after v2.1.0):"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:36
msgid "python scripts bench --untested_tags"
msgstr "python scripts bench --untested_tags"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:40
msgid "测试指定标签："
msgstr "Test specified tags:"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:42
msgid "python scripts bench --tags v2.1.0 v2.2.0"
msgstr "python scripts bench --tags v2.1.0 v2.2.0"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:46
msgid "使用指定哈希测试并自动打开预览："
msgstr "Test with specified hashes and automatically open the preview:"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:48
msgid "python scripts bench --hashes 78b7c20 2c1fcfd -o"
msgstr "python scripts bench --hashes 78b7c20 2c1fcfd -o"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:52
msgid "你也可以直接使用 ``asv preview -b`` 在本地预览已经发布的结果。"
msgstr "You can also directly use ``asv preview -b`` to preview published results locally."

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:55
msgid "脚本行为说明"
msgstr "Script Behavior"

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:57
msgid ""
"当使用 ``--untested_tags`` 时，脚本会查询仓库中自 v2.1.0 之后的 tag 的对应哈希（项目内部实现位于 ``scripts/bench/"
"hashes.py``），并与已测试的哈希进行比对，只对尚未测试的提交运行基准。"
msgstr ""
"When ``--untested_tags`` is used, the script queries hashes for tags since v2.1.0 in the repository (the internal "
"implementation is in ``scripts/bench/hashes.py``), compares them against already tested hashes, and runs benchmarks only "
"for untested commits."

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:58
msgid "如果同时传入 ``--tags`` 或 ``--hashes``，也会将它们加入待测哈希列表。"
msgstr "If ``--tags`` or ``--hashes`` are also provided, they will be added to the hash list to be tested as well."

#: ../../source/development/bench.rst:59
msgid ""
"在开始运行前，脚本会把要测试的哈希列表写入 ``.asv/_tag_hashes.txt``，并调用 ``asv run HASHFILE:.asv/_tag_hashes.txt`` 运行"
"基准用例，随后使用 ``asv publish`` 将结果发布到本地，最后（可选）调用 ``asv preview -b`` 打开浏览器预览。"
msgstr ""
"Before execution starts, the script writes the hash list to be tested into ``.asv/_tag_hashes.txt``, runs benchmark cases "
"via ``asv run HASHFILE:.asv/_tag_hashes.txt``, then publishes results locally with ``asv publish``, and finally "
"(optionally) opens a browser preview with ``asv preview -b``."
